            <div class="home-content">
                <div class="page_info">
                                            <h1>“CNC technology should not be the privilege of a few. It should be the affordable strength of all.”</h1>
                                                                        <h3>With this ideology,  Askar Group was born. Askar Microns a part of Group, manufactures CNC machines at an affordable price to the customers. ‘SPINNER’ series (which is a registered trade mark of ASKAR), Spin turn Series, Spin Flat Series, Smart Mill Series, Spin Train Series etc., are the product names of Askar CNC Machines.

Askar CNC Machines are designed and built with the latest design concepts and at a manufacturing facility which meets the global standards. Askar incorporates all international features required for a CNC machine and meets the global standards in latest machine tool technology.</h3>
                                                </div>
                <div class="clear"></div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                    <div class="grid_8 alpha">
                        <div class="feature-content-inner first">
                            <div class="image-box">
                                                                    <a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spinner-15/"><img src="http://askarmicron.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/sp15-3.jpg" alt="First Feature Image" /></a>
                                <a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spinner-15/ "><div class="mask"></div></a></div>
                            <div class="feature-content-text">
                                <h3><a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spinner-15/">Slant Saddle Series </a></h3>
                                                                                                    <p>Rigid Turning Center

The robust machine structure of Spinner15 supports best surface finish and high metal cutting capability with high accuracy for medium diameter components.

Control System

Standard System package :- SINUMERIK-828D
Option System package :- FANUC 0iMate TD
</p>
                                                                <a class="read-more" href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spinner-15/">Read More</a></div> </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid_8">
                        <div class="feature-content-inner second">
                            <div class="image-box">
                                                                    <a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spin-flat/"><img src="http://askarmicron.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/sf20001.jpg" alt="First Feature Image" /></a>
                                <a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spin-flat/"><div class="mask"></div></a></div>
                            <div class="feature-content-text">
                                <h3><a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spin-flat/">Flat Bed Series </a></h3>
                                                                                                    <p>Heavy Duty Flat Bed Turning Center

Spin Flat is flat bed turning center with the range from 1000 to 3000 ABC. Spin Flat is ideally suited for heavy and lengthy jobs, maximum swing over bed of 700mm. Spin Flat is specially designed for machining of lengthy and heavy jobs.

Control System

Standard System package :- SINUMERIK – 828D SL
Option System Package     :- FANUC 0iMate TC
</p>
                                                                <a class="read-more" href="http://askarmicron.co.in/spin-flat/">Read More</a></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class=" grid_8 omega">
                        <div class="feature-content-inner third">
                            <div class="image-box">
                                                                <a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/smart-mill-600/"><img src="http://askarmicron.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VMC.jpg" alt="First Feature Image" /></a>
                                <a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/smart-mill-600/"><div class="mask"></div></a></div>
                            <div class="feature-content-text">
                            <h3><a href="http://askarmicron.co.in/smart-mill-600/">Vertical Machining Center</a></h3>
                                                                                                        <p>Smart mill-600

The machine concept of the Smart mill series convinces by compact design, High rigidity through box structured base & column design with highest quality. ASKAR now brings to you the smart mill series of VMCs with features such as 8,000 rpm spindle with CTS, tool magazine 20 tools with double gripper ATC, side chip conveyor with built in coolant system, high rapid traverses and high-tech controls.</p>
